          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Making FHA More Affordable Act of 2017 </b></p> <p>This bill amends the National Housing Act to require Federal Housing Administration mortgage borrowers to pay mortgage insurance premiums only when their remaining principal balance exceeds&nbsp;78% or more of the home value or sales price. </p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2017-10-26T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <name>Introduced in House</name>
        </item>
